# RootAISpec  – Silicon Atlas
stack: Vite + React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind + Visx + D3
folder-layout:
  src/
    components/
    hooks/
    data/
    pages/
  public/
conventions:
  • Use functional React components with named exports.
  • State lives in Zustand; avoid Redux.
  • Tailwind class order → “padding->layout->color->motion”.
  • Dates stored as ISO-8601 strings.
  • Each component gets a `<name>.test.tsx` with RTL + Vitest.
eslint: use Airbnb + Prettier.